<script type='text/javascript'>//<![CDATA[
window.onload=function(){
$(document).ready(function() {
	var titles = ["Home", 1, "Menu", 3, "History", 5, "Contact", 7]
  var description = ["<p>Welcome to Mama's Stone Bowl. We are a small mom-and-pop restaurant located in the heart of Seattle. Our mission is to mesh quality and authenticity in every dish.</p> <p>We love our Korean food as well as our Korean culture and we hope that you will too.Enjoy!</p>", "<p>Mama's Classic Stone Pot : $10</p><P>Mama's Seafood Stone Pot : $10</P><p>Mama's Island Style Stone Pot : $10</p><p>Mama's Ox Tail Soup : $8</p>", "<p>The dohl-sot easily translated as 'stone bowl' was and continues to be a staple way to serve an all time favorite Korean Dish - BiBimBap. Commonly referred to as dohl-sot bibimbap, the dish has widespread fame in America. Consisting of rice, steamed to perfection, a mixture of vegetables including seasoned spinach, bean sprouts, cabbage, aged kimchee, heaping serving of marinated beef and a beautiful egg cooked to absolute perfection. The bowl is prepared over heat in order to cook the rice to a crisp offering an amazing seasoned rice cracker at the end of the meal. The bowl will be expertly mixed using a well-seasoned korean pepper paste in addition an absolutely perfect serving of earthy sesame oil. Mouth watering!</p>", "<p>Telephone: (206) 867-5309</p><p>Address: 123 Main Street</p><p>Seattle, Washington 98301</p><p>Come join us!</p>"]
  
  $("#content").append('<h1>Mama\'s Stone Bowl</h1>');
  $("h1").after('<div id="crop">');
  $("#crop").append('<img src="http://foodnetwork.sndimg.com/content/dam/images/food/fullset/2015/1/15/0/FNM_030115-Simple-Seoul-Bibimbap-Recipe_s4x3.jpg" />');
  $("#crop").after('<ul>');
	for(var i = 1; i<=8; i+=2) {
  	$('ul').append('<li class="tabs" id="a'+titles[i]+'">'+titles[i-1]+'</li');
  };
  
  for(var j = 1; j<=4; j++) {
  	$('ul').after("<div class='tab_desc' id='a"+j*2+"'>"+description[j-1]+"</div>");
  };
  
  $(".tabs").click(function() {
    var elId = $(this).attr("id");
    $(".tab_desc").stop().fadeOut().promise().done(function() {
      switch (elId) {
        case "a1":
          $("#a2").fadeIn(500);
          break;
        case "a3":
          $("#a4").fadeIn(500);
          break;
        case "a5":
          $("#a6").fadeIn(500);
          break;
        case "a7":
          $("#a8").fadeIn(500);
          break;
      }
    });
  });

});

